**Network and Datacenter Information**  
Our Detroit VPS services are hosted at [123.NET](http://123.net) in Southfield, MI, just minutes from Detroit.
We operate our own network utilizing a fully redundant architecture. Upstream peers include the following:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10G Level 3 (Southfield, MI)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10G Global Crossing (Chicago, IL)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10G Cogent (Southfield, MI)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10G CenturyLink/Saavis (Ashburn, VA)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2.5G Comcast (Chicago, IL)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
We also own and operate our own [ASN](http://bgp.he.net/AS62588) - feel free to contact us if you need a BGP session or want to announce your own IP space!
   
     
